race.description: Thunderbolt Equine In Memory Of J Blanch Mdn Hcp
race.comment: ABATED BREATH (2) missed the placings on debut two runs back then got a long way back last start when 4 lengths away in fifth over 1280m at Muswellbrook. Faces an easier assignment so he is sure to be prominent. NUCLEAIRE (4) has been in the betting at both starts but hasn't managed to live up to market expectations. Most recently finished sixth over 1300m at Dubbo, beaten 1.75 lengths. Among the leading chances on his best figures. TOURTEL (1) turned in an eye-catching run over 1300m at this track last time, ridden back before coming home with a powerful run to finish third. Expected to feature again. BRIDE WARS (7) is back after a break of four-and-a-half months. Finished eighth over 1100m at Bathurst on June 19. Nicely placed and can figure in the finish.
